#### Sizes

| Size | Dimensions | Usage |
|------|------------|-------|
| sm | 96px | Inline, compact |
| md | 144-176px | Card headers |
| lg | 192-224px | Landing hero |
| xl | 256-320px | Full-screen focus |

### 3.2 Glassmorphism Cards

#### Glass Variants

```css
/* Standard glass */
.glass {
  background: hsl(var(--background) / 0.7);
  backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
  border: 1px solid hsl(var(--border) / 0.5);
}

/* Card glass - slightly more opaque */
.glass-card {
  background: hsl(var(--card) / 0.8);
  backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
  box-shadow: 0 4px 24px hsl(var(--foreground) / 0.06),
              inset 0 1px 0 hsl(0 0% 100% / 0.1);
}

/* Capsule glass - input fields */
.capsule-glass {
  background: hsl(var(--card) / 0.6);
  backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
  border: 1px solid hsl(var(--border) / 0.4);
}

/* Hyper glass - navigation, overlays */
.hyper-glass {
  background: hsl(var(--card) / 0.7);
  backdrop-filter: blur(24px);
  border: 1px solid hsl(var(--border) / 0.6);
}
```

