| Icon | Function | Behavior |
|------|----------|----------|
| ğŸ’¬ | Text input | Default mode |
| ğŸ¤ | Voice input | Hold to record, release to send |
| ğŸ“· | Image/Photo | Gallery picker or camera |
| ğŸ˜Š | Quick mood | Emoji picker for instant mood log |

